Package: RashaFinal
Type: Package
Title: Mixture Normal Distribution and Weather Simulation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rasha Alsaadawi
Maintainer: Rasha Alsaadawi <alsaadawir@vcu.edu>
Description: The package has two functions: mix_norm and weather_simulator; mix_norm takes  five arguments (p,mu1,mu2,sigma1,sigma2) to sample Y from the mixture normal distribution; weather_simulator takes inthe weather today (sunny/rainy) and simulates the weather condition and rainfall in inches for the next 10 days.
